The focus on the correlation between objectives suggests a connection to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), while the use of metaheuristics and optimization techniques suggests a connection to neural networks (cs.NE), data structures (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the analysis of the search space and the design of benchmark problems suggest a connection to data mining (cs.DM).
